{"tid":245963,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲網民排出近十年作品最喜愛夢想情人女角頭十位","createTime":"2017-05-16T15:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T11:12:11.000Z","uid":6327,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc4cc15310f9d4cab7489430ad90a58aa151357","tid":245963,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/232656_dbc8bc69b034c660e85306b48f50441d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F232656_dbc8bc69b034c660e85306b48f50441d.jpg&h=62c1ac2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1.不破愛花</span><br />\n出自：絕園的暴風雨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/233052_11768e40098165da4dd1a5395aa80e7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F233052_11768e40098165da4dd1a5395aa80e7e.jpg&h=64a0cac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.椎名真由理<br />\n出自：命運石之門0<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-KjFpxyKBz6Q/VNclmNWJ5jI/AAAAAAAAAEc/HmwH3t8BjHI/w506-h285/Nisekoi%2Bova.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-KjFpxyKBz6Q%2FVNclmNWJ5jI%2FAAAAAAAAAEc%2FHmwH3t8BjHI%2Fw506-h285%2FNisekoi%252Bova.gif&h=3c2184a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">3.小野寺小咲</span> <br />\n出自：偽戀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/233455_233adb5930404136e01c1eeb1858b613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F233455_233adb5930404136e01c1eeb1858b613.jpg&h=aadb49d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.五更琉璃<br />\n出自：我的妹妹哪有這麼可愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/233818_1e156587906748640f021a27bc99384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F233818_1e156587906748640f021a27bc99384f.jpg&h=151f529b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.柴崎蘆花 <br />\n出自：屬性同好會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/233909_fa2bd23ed9420bbbcc1cc101be59e99a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F233909_fa2bd23ed9420bbbcc1cc101be59e99a.jpg&h=3d00dc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6.河合律<br />\n出自：我們大家的河合莊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/233953_a45673c78a89f914f86699073f3816ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F233953_a45673c78a89f914f86699073f3816ec.jpg&h=910b4f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.羽瀨川小鳩<br />\n出自：我的朋友很少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/234223_33b2391cc065a59349648efd0adbd49b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F234223_33b2391cc065a59349648efd0adbd49b.jpg&h=b2eefcdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8.常守朱<br />\n出自：psycho-pass<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/234337_258884b796b13f1b0ebe0ea59e3d5ec4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F234337_258884b796b13f1b0ebe0ea59e3d5ec4.jpg&h=32b427d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9.綠川花<br />\n出自：監獄校園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/234421_38fd5737e07ffff4f3ca6bd0ff030510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F234421_38fd5737e07